MusicPlayerService/
├── Models/ # Data models
├── Sources/ # Different music sources
├── ViewModels/ # Playback logic with Combine
├── Views/ # SwiftUI User Interface
├── Managers/ # Singleton Playback Manager
└── MusicPlayerServiceApp.swift


---

## ⚙️ Technologies Used

- **Swift 5.9+**
- **Xcode 15+**
- **iOS 15+**
- **SwiftUI + Combine**
- **MVVM Architecture**
- **Design Patterns:** Singleton, Strategy

---

## 🎮 Features

| Feature               | Description                                       |
|----------------------|---------------------------------------------------|
| 🎶 Multiple Sources   | Local Files & Spotify mock source                 |
| ▶️ Playback Control   | Play, Pause, Stop                                 |
| 🧠 Playback Manager   | Singleton that controls track & state             |
| 🔁 Playlist Queue     | View + tap to play from list                      |
| 🔄 Combine Updates    | Tracks and states updated reactively              |
| 🎨 SwiftUI UI         | Clean and minimal interface                       |

